description: When this boy called me, he told me that he can´t afford to talk for too long. In that second I knew I was going to have some fun today. My new friend was 21 years old and from a small town in the East. He moved to Prague and started working at a bar. His financial situation was getting worse every day. He needed 28 000 to put his budget in order and pay all his debts. I was really horny today so I decided not to make things easy for him and basically didn´t give him any other option than my naughty proposition. He agreed and we had a great time. Young and adorable boy turned into a dirty sell-out bitch. I love corrupting innocent youngsters. It´s probably the second best thing about my hobby. After fucking those straight asses of course.
title: Debt Dandy 246
